          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold">Email</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-3">The best way to reach me</p>
          <a href="mailto:chikanda120@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline font-medium">
            chikanda120@gmail.com
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border bg-card p-6">
          <div class="mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold">Response Time</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            I typically respond within 48 hours. For urgent matters, please mention it in your email subject line.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border bg-card p-6">
          <div class="mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold">What to Reach Out About</h3>
          <ul class="text-muted-foreground space-y-1 text-sm">
            <li>- Questions about tools or reviews</li>
            <li>- Business inquiries or partnerships</li>
            <li>- Content suggestions</li>
            <li>- Feedback on the website</li>
            <li>- General questions about solopreneurship</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border bg-card p-8">
        <h2 class="mb-6 text-xl font-bold">Send a Message</h2>
        <form action="mailto:chikanda120@gmail.com" method="post" enctype="text/plain" class="space-y-4">
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <label for="name" class="text-sm font-medium">Name</label>
            <input
              type="text"
              id="name"
              name="name"
              required
              class="w-full rounded-lg border bg-background px-4 py-2 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary"
              placeholder="Your name"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-2">
            <label for="email" class="text-sm font-medium">Email</label>
            <input
              type="email"
              id="email"
              name="email"
              required
              class="w-full rounded-lg border bg-background px-4 py-2 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary"
              placeholder="your@email.com"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-2">
            <label for="subject" class="text-sm font-medium">Subject</label>
            <input
              type="text"
              id="subject"
              name="subject"
              required
              class="w-full rounded-lg border bg-background px-4 py-2 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary"
              placeholder="What's this about?"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-2">
            <label for="message" class="text-sm font-medium">Message</label>
            <textarea
              id="message"
              name="message"
              rows="5"
              required
              class="w-full rounded-lg border bg-background px-4 py-2 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary"
              placeholder="Your message..."
            ></textarea>
          </div>

          <button
            type="submit"
            class="w-full rounded-lg bg-primary px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors"
          >
            Send Message
          </button>
        </form>

        <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-muted-foreground text-center">
          Or email me directly at <a href="mailto:chikanda120@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">chikanda120@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
